{"type": "article", "id": 20754, "title": "nendo 便签纸和软面抄", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-15T07:17:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150842zGPdV5YfSTAtXm1j.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 nendo 最新推出的便签纸和软面抄。便签纸有三种型号：正方形和两种大小的长方形。它们巧妙地拼在一个带缺口的正方体中，用白色的塑料做依托，也可以侧着放在桌上。软面抄有 Left 和 Right 两种，对应了两种内页，在右下角带有圆点的和横线、圆点、空白的组合。封面有黑白两色，是极简风格的设计。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150840yqO6UsxkwT3VHta9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6207265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150840EMcvmxPsNhXBpn1L.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150841FT2Wk4sRupOhqQHB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.77029915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150841g9dofJDYC6A3iHwb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6292735\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150841GCdPiENYBabxkHfp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}